{"tid":1083824,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有人問我 我就會講 我是中國人","createTime":"2019-03-30T02:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:43:00.000Z","uid":5649,"like":28,"dislike":117,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"721c3354b51bc35dff69858148a73fc164407921","tid":1083824,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"我期待中華人民共和國 可擊敗美國<br />\n我的心情猶像樽蓋 等被揭開 咀巴卻在養青苔<br />\n人潮內 愈愛國 愈變得 不受理睬 自己要搞出意外<br />\n像突然 地高歌 中華人民共和國萬萬歲<br />\n著最閃的衫 扮十分感慨 有人來拍照要記住插袋<br />\n<br />\n你當我是中國人 愛國只因我很怕<br />\n似木頭 似石頭的話 得到注意嗎<br />\n其實怕被忘記 至放大來演吧<br />\n很不安 怎去優雅<br />\n世上還讚頌沉默嗎<br />\n不夠爆炸 怎麼有話題 讓我誇 做個中國人"},{"pid":"f9e8e8da94ad0067b0c0fa0127a3acdebce4045d","tid":1083824,"uid":45977,"like":53,"dislike":8,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vW9FDfO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvW9FDfO.gif&h=a5d0acc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"977d5825cdc256e53f15d376558364eb9adcadf3","tid":1083824,"uid":43557,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:40:16.000Z","msg":"喊能左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9980d50bd2da831da1e5bd7e014e80f8a52c5c09","tid":1083824,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4f30531cc59c9b0d1fcef7a4b7ef20c8017b07","tid":1083824,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"2f3ba753a39817fdb62087d8ef39c700cba007c9","tid":1083824,"uid":243093,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:55:07.000Z","msg":"我期待中華人民共和國 可擊敗美國<br />\n<br />\n呢句勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3973ced328b92ab6a693a053464c07e4cce0bc9","tid":1083824